With this function you can customize post excerpt

1. Change lenght for excerpt
2. Set value of letters - ex: return 14; show 14 letters of excerpt

-----> Copy and paste it on functions.php from line 8 to line 11 (supp. that you write on <?php ;?>)

function custom_excerpt_length( $length ) {
    return 14;
}
add_filter( 'excerpt_length', 'custom_excerpt_length', 999 );
